<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />

    <style>
      {% if font_path %}
      @font-face {
        font-family: 'Custom';
        src: url('{{ font_path }}');
      }
      {% endif %}

      .main {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 25px;
        width: fit-content;
        background: url('./bg.jpg') local center/cover no-repeat;
        font-family: Custom, sans-serif;
      }

      .main * {
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 80px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .main p {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 30px;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .table {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .table table {
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 30px;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        border-style: hidden;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
      }

      .table td,
      th {
        border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        padding: 15px 10px;
      }

      .table th {
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      div.table {
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        width: calc(100% - 50px);
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 15px;
      }

      .title {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      {% for i, h in enumerate(heads) %}
      .t-{{ i }} {
        text-align: {{ h.align }};
        {% if h.min_width %}min-width: {{ h.min_width }}px;{% endif %}
        {% if h.max_width %}max-width: {{ h.max_width }}px;{% endif %}
      }
      {% endfor %}
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="main">
      <h1 class="title">{{ calling }}列表</h1>
      <p class="header">
        Tip：<strong>发送序号</strong> 选择{{ calling }} |
        发送 <strong>P</strong>+<strong>数字</strong> 跳到指定页数<br />
        其他操作：<strong>上一页</strong>(P) | <strong>下一页</strong>(N) |
        <strong>退出</strong>(E)
      </p>

      <div class="table">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              {% for i, h in enumerate(heads) %}
              <th class="t-{{ i }}">{{ h.name }}</th>
              {% endfor %}
            </tr>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            {% for line in lines %}
            <tr>
              {% for i, t in enumerate(line) %}
              <td class="t-{{ i }}">{{ t }}</td>
              {% endfor %}
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p class="footer">
        第 <strong>{{ current_page }}</strong> /
        <strong>{{ max_page }}</strong> 页 | 共
        <strong>{{ max_count }}</strong> 首
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
